title: Spliced Business Formations within 8 Quarters for Vermont (DISCONTINUED)
notes:
The Business Formation Statistics are now released on a monthly basis, and the quarterly series will no longer be updated. See BFSBF8QTOTALNSAVT (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BFSBF8QTOTALNSAVT) for an alternative.

This series combines (splices) https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BF8QNSAVT and https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/PBF8QNSAVT to provide the entire time series for the actual and projected business formations within 8 quarters.
